headline: Honeywell Mulls A Move That May Herald Aerospace Megamerger
summary: A standalone Honeywell aerospace business could be worth up to $120 billion. Honeywell stock rose on Monday.

headline: 3 Reasons to Sell MMM and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: 3M’s 29.1% return over the past six months has outpaced the S&P 500 by 18.6%, and its stock price has climbed to $129.75 per share. This run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
